INSERT INTO emlog_blog VALUES('7','主客户端 Welcome to YouHosting.com','1416579561','<p style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;font:14px/23px \'lucida Grande\', Verdana, \'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;color:#000000;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	Dear aimidada aimidada,\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;font:14px/23px \'lucida Grande\', Verdana, \'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;color:#000000;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	Thank you for signing up with YouHosting! Your account has been activated and you can login to the administration area by using the details below.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;font:14px/23px \'lucida Grande\', Verdana, \'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;color:#000000;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	Email:<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"outline-style:none;outline-color:invert;outline-width:medium;color:#3d5e86;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:underline;\" href=\"mailto:aimidada@foxmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">aimidada@fox<wbr>mail.com</a><br />\r\nPassword:*********\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;font:14px/23px \'lucida Grande\', Verdana, \'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;color:#000000;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	Login at:<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"outline-style:none;outline-color:invert;outline-width:medium;color:#3d5e86;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:underline;\" href=\"http://youhosting.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://youhosting.com</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;font:14px/23px \'lucida Grande\', Verdana, \'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;color:#000000;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	*** How to get started? ***\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;font:14px/23px \'lucida Grande\', Verdana, \'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;color:#000000;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	1. Point your master domain to our name servers or setup your own private name servers.<br />\r\nYou can find name server setup instructions on \"Configuration -&gt; Name Server Settings\" section. You can use our default *.main-hosting.com name servers for all your domains or you can setup your own, private name servers.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;font:14px/23px \'lucida Grande\', Verdana, \'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;color:#000000;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	2. Setup a website from where you will provide web hosting services.<br />\r\nWe have prepared you a few simple website templates that can be installed to your master account. Click on the \"Look and Feel -&gt; Install Main Website\" section, choose a template, enter your master account FTP password and website will be installed. You can use File Manager or FTP client to download website files to your computer and make modifications. Finally you will need to integrate client sign up form. Client sign up form example can be obtained form the \"Look and Feel -&gt; Client Sign Up Form\" section. Paste it on your order page and you will be able to start accepting new client registrations!\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;font:14px/23px \'lucida Grande\', Verdana, \'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;color:#000000;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	3. Setup feature sets and hosting plans.<br />\r\nA feature set allows you to control which features to offer for your clients. For example if you would like to disable MySQL, just uncheck the \"MySQL\" box when configuring a feature set. To setup feature sets click on the \"Configuration -&gt; Manage Feature Sets\" section.<br />\r\nA hosting plan can limit resources assigned for each account. To manage hosting plan click on the \"Configuration -&gt; Manage Hosting Plans\" section.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;font:14px/23px \'lucida Grande\', Verdana, \'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;color:#000000;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	4. Configure payment gateways.<br />\r\nIf you plan to sell paid hosting plans you need to have an active PayPal or 2checkout.com account. All payments will be made to your accounts and orders activated automatically. Click on the \"Configuration -&gt; Manage Payment Gateways\" section to setup how your clients will pay you.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;font:14px/23px \'lucida Grande\', Verdana, \'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;color:#000000;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	Need help? Please submit a ticket to YouHosting staff from the \"Support -&gt; YouHosting Tickets\" section.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;font:14px/23px \'lucida Grande\', Verdana, \'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;color:#000000;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	YouHosting.com\r\n</p>','','master-client','1','-1','page','0','0','0','n','n','n','y','n','','');
